 45→/// A tool that spawns a sub-agent running its own agent loop.
 46→///
 47→/// The sub-agent executes synchronously (blocks until done) and its result
 48→/// is returned as the tool output. Sub-agents get a filtered copy of the
 49→/// parent's tool registry (without the `spawn_agent` tool itself) and a
 50→/// focused system prompt.
 51→/// Callback for emitting events from the sub-agent back to the parent UI.
 52→pub type OnSpawnEvent = Arc<dyn Fn(RunnerEvent) + Send + Sync>;
